      <heading>Thu Aug 10 (Jasurin)    :: &amp;gRank Listing&amp;n</heading>
      <slot>2</slot>
      <level>203</level>
      <author>0</author>
      <date>0</date>
      <text>The following progressions/unique ranks are available in the Hunter guild:

Oathtaker Hunter/Huntress, Experienced, Renowned, Legendary

Student of the Blade, Swordsman, Skilled Swordsman, Champion

Footpad, Cutpurse, Thief, Rogue, Infamous

Retainer, Servant, High Servant, Advisor

Informant, Detective, Sleuth, Chalk Talker

Lord/Lady
Minor Lord/Lady

Thieftaker
Notorius
Captain
Spy
Guard
Servant
Mercenary
Assassin
Prophet of the Horn
Prophetess of the Horn
Blademaster
Cartographer
Chronicler of the Great Hunt
Master/Mistress of the Hunt

Any rank in the first two levels of any progression may be claimed by any
member of the guild, after a short period of settling in.  Beyond that,
any higher ranks will be awarded at the GL's discretion, based on what
progress a character may have made towards Glory and Renown.  The final
rank in each and every one of the progressions will most likely require
a great deal of roleplay, a particularly exciting character, and also
some small degree of reputatation among the rest of the MUD's populace.
They will be -extremely- rare, denoting those Hunters whose reputation
and accomplishments have earned them a place in the legends, in some
small degree.

-&amp;YJ&amp;ya&amp;Ys&amp;yu&amp;Yr&amp;yi&amp;Yn&amp;n
</text>
